# prisma
# NOTE: /prisma/migrations must stay committed — migrations are source code, and
# the deploy applies them. They were ignored here until 2026-07-15, so 11
# migrations ran against production and were never checked in; the schema then
# drifted and `prisma db push` became the only way to apply changes, which
# silently rewrites production to match schema.prisma. Do not re-add this.
/prisma/backups

